      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of extraordinary caliber, preserved in impeccable showroom condition. This vehicle exemplifies meticulous stewardship, featuring a flawless exterior finish and an interior cabin that remains in a state of absolute refinement. Engineered for the most discerning collector, it offers an unparalleled driving experience and serves as a definitive benchmark for its class. We invite you to acquire this masterpiece of mechanical and aesthetic integrity, representing the pinnacle of its lineage.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
