      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting a true collector-grade masterpiece in absolute showroom condition. This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, preserving its flawless original paint and deep, mirror-like luster. The interior is immaculate, featuring supple, uncreased leather and a cabin that still carries a new-car aroma. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach; every service has been performed ahead of schedule by certified specialists, with a comprehensive folder of records included. From the pristine engine bay to the untouched undercarriage, no detail has been overlooked. This is a rare opportunity to own a specimen that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the dealership floor.",
      "price": 46500.0,
