    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, this car is in such incredible shape it still looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered since day one\u2014not a single scratch or speck of dust anywhere. I\u2019ve loved every mile in it, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy this beauty. You won't find another one this clean, I promise! Come take a look and see for yourself!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
